      <title>中东财富基金因领导层变动而受到冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-15/middle-east-wealth-funds-jolted-by-leadership-changes-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔为其 5100 亿美元的基金任命了一位新首席执行官，而科威特则更换了其 1 万亿美元国家支持投资者的负责人。彭博社的 Adveith Nair 报道了这些变化的影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-15/middle-east-wealth-funds-jolted-by-leadership-changes-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 05:40:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
