    <item>
      <title>渣打银行依靠富裕的非洲人推动增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/standard-chartered-s-leaning-on-wealthy-africans-to-drive-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行在非洲大陆的财富业务管理资产规模过去三年增长了一倍以上，目前正依靠非洲的超级富豪来扩大其业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/standard-chartered-s-leaning-on-wealthy-africans-to-drive-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 05:17:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡房屋销售因郊区需求创 11 个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/singapore-home-sales-reach-11-month-high-on-suburban-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了抓住需求回升的机会，开发商在郊区释放了更多库存，新加坡住房销售额因此升至近一年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/singapore-home-sales-reach-11-month-high-on-suburban-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 04:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受供应过剩担忧和美元走低影响，油价本周下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国经济和消费数据好坏参半、美元走强的持续影响以及对明年全球市场将陷入供过于求的担忧，油价下跌，加剧了本周的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 23:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
